PrecisEnactment of the FEDERAL HALOCARBON REGULATIONS which are designed to ensure that action is taken to prevent the release of ozone-depleting substances, to report releases, to provide adequate training to personnel and to develop emergency procedures and strategic plans for the use, control and gradual elimination of these substances.

precis:
Enactment of the FEDERAL HALOCARBON REGULATIONS which are designed to
ensure that action is taken to prevent the release of ozone-depleting
substances, to report releases, to provide adequate training to personnel
and to develop emergency procedures and strategic plans for the use,
control and gradual elimination of these substances.
